{"title":"Combine your love of streetwear and cycling with the MAAP × New Era cycling cap","link":"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/maap-x-new-era-cycling-cap/","date":1617279624000,"content":"<img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/MAAPxNEWERA_BONE-1-9ff9f3f.jpg?quality=90&#038;resize=620,413\" srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/MAAPxNEWERA_BONE-1-9ff9f3f.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=960,639 960w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/MAAPxNEWERA_BONE-1-9ff9f3f.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=720,479 720w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/MAAPxNEWERA_BONE-1-9ff9f3f.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=576,383 576w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/MAAPxNEWERA_BONE-1-9ff9f3f.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=360,239 360w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/04/MAAPxNEWERA_BONE-1-9ff9f3f.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=180,119 180w, \" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" class=\"wp-image-624804 alignnone size-landscape_thumbnail\" alt=\"MAAP × New Era cycling cap\" title=\"MAAPxNEWERA_BONE-1\" />                                            <p>Australian cycling kit brand MAAP has teamed up with American purveyor of fashionable urban hats New Era to “reimagine” the cycling cap.</p>\n<p>The Stealth Performance Cap is designed for the hottest riding conditions and the two brands claim to have redesigned the ubiquitous cycling cap using “cutting edge technology”.</p>\n<p>It costs €35 / AU$50, comes in three designs, and uses breathable, wicking fabrics with laser-cut perforations for air flow, and an internal sweatband to keep perspiration from running where it shouldn’t.</p>\n<div class=\"image-handler__container image-handler__container--aspect\" style=\"padding-bottom: calc(100% / 1.501210653753);\">\n    <picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\